title: Staying Safe
description:
Pablo Torre and Domonique Foxworth discuss their reactions to Tua leaving Thursday Night Football on a stretcher. Then The Ringer's Kevin Clark and The Athletic's Nate Tice join to talk if we crowned the Eagles too early and preview Bucs-Chiefs. Plus, can Russ and the Broncos get going against the Raiders?
